 a final score of 16.200 points.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9991683721395865, \"rank\": 0.0007222933563244423, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Jingyuan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zou Jingyuan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Jingyuan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Jingyuan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukraine's Illia Kovtun claimed silver with a score of 15.500, earning his nation's first gymnastics medal since 2016.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9768318467032795, \"rank\": 0.023185763423817903, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illia_Kovtun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Illia Kovtun\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illia_Kovtun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illia_Kovtun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bronze went to Japan's Shinnosuke Oka, as the men's all-around champion earned his maiden parallel bars medal with 15.300 points.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.6836041957889784, \"rank\": 0.4383281067494051, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinnosuke_Oka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shinnosuke Oka\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinnosuke_Oka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinnosuke_Oka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zou's compatriot Zhang Boheng narrowly missed the podium, finishing in fourth place.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Department\", \"score\": 0.623957349446136, \"rank\": 0.485020926313336, \"text\": \"Zou\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Department\"}, {\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhang Boheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zou's victory marks the 21st gold for the Chinese delegation at the Paris Summer Olympics, and the second for the country's gymnastics team in the French capital.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Department\", \"score\": 0.623957349446136, \"rank\": 0.485020926313336, \"text\": \"Zou\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zou_Department\"}, {\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.8939457281620233, \"rank\": 0.11681857421543453, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}